I"o
<p>Replace $x$ with $-x$,</p>

\[\begin{align*}
	F(-x) &amp;= \frac{8}{(-x)^2+3} \\
		&amp;= \frac{8}{x^2+3} \\
	F(-x) &amp;= F(x)
\end{align*}\]

<p>Hence, the function is <strong>Even</strong></p>

